Package org.sbml.jsbml.ext.fbc.converters

Class GPRParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sbml.jsbml.ext.fbc.converters.GPRParser

  • public class GPRParser
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides a method to converts gene association string as used in COBRA in SBML level 2 into GeneProductAssociation used in SBML level 3.

    The conversion modify directly the arguments so clone them beforehand if needed. The SBML level is not changed so that's also something that need to be done before calling the method parseGPR(Reaction, String, boolean)

    Since:
    1.3
    Author:
    Andreas Dräger
